‎The heartfelt appeal of that song

00:54:55.141 --> 00:54:58.244 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎brings to mind the words of Isaiah 41:10,

00:54:58.244 --> 00:55:00.280 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎where we’re encouraged:

00:55:00.280 --> 00:55:03.783 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎“Do not be afraid, for I am with you. 

00:55:03.783 --> 00:55:07.454 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
