00:55:20.266 --> 00:55:22.268 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎and from fellow believers

00:55:22.268 --> 00:55:25.271 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎to resist being molded by this system.

00:55:26.673 --> 00:55:29.242 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎To conclude, 
we bring you greetings

00:55:29.242 --> 00:55:32.078 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎from Maraã, 
in the state of Amazonas

00:55:32.078 --> 00:55:34.647 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎in northern Brazil. 

00:55:34.647 --> 00:55:38.518 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Nestled in the Amazon rain forest
along the Japurá River,

00:55:38.518 --> 00:55:41.321 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎there are no roads leading to this city;

00:55:41.321 --> 00:55:44.991 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎it can only be reached by river. 

00:55:44.991 --> 00:55:48.995 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎For most travelers, 
reaching the city is a three-day journey,

00:55:48.995 --> 00:55:52.999 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎which involves sleeping 
in hammocks along the way. 

00:55:52.999 --> 00:55:56.703 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Around 18,000 people inhabit the area,

00:55:56.703 --> 00:55:58.872 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎but because of its remote location,

00:55:58.872 --> 00:56:03.576 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎many people have never had 
the opportunity to hear the good news.

00:56:03.576 --> 00:56:07.180 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎With that in mind, 
along with several other cities,

00:56:08.548 --> 00:56:12.385 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Maraã was included 
in the Amazonas national preaching campaign.

00:56:12.385 --> 00:56:16.689 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎The goal of this special campaign
was to reach the thousands of people

00:56:16.689 --> 00:56:20.627 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎who live in some 
of Amazon’s most isolated areas.

00:56:20.627 --> 00:56:23.063 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎As a result, 
many willing brothers and sisters

00:56:23.063 --> 00:56:27.967 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎moved here to serve 
where the need is greater.

00:56:27.967 --> 00:56:31.104 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Since the city 
is completely surrounded by rivers,

00:56:31.104 --> 00:56:35.442 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎publishers reach interested ones by boat. 

00:56:35.442 --> 00:56:39.279 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Special pioneers have played 
a large part in cultivating interest

00:56:39.279 --> 00:56:42.682 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎by using this method of preaching.

00:56:42.682 --> 00:56:46.119 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎One of the 23 congregations that was formed

00:56:46.119 --> 00:56:48.288 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎as a result of the special campaign

00:56:48.288 --> 00:56:51.458 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎is located here. 

00:56:51.458 --> 00:56:54.861 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Today, 
more than 20 publishers in the congregation

00:56:54.861 --> 00:56:59.265 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎are conducting at least 100 Bible studies. 

00:56:59.265 --> 00:57:03.002 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎And we’re happy to report that in 2017

00:57:03.002 --> 00:57:06.840 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎the first local family was baptized. 

00:57:06.840 --> 00:57:10.210 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎Our dear brothers and sisters
are working hard to help

00:57:10.210 --> 00:57:13.480 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎those in the Amazon region
to learn about Jehovah,

00:57:13.480 --> 00:57:15.482 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎and they send their warm love

00:57:15.482 --> 00:57:17.550 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎and greetings to all of us

00:57:17.550 --> 00:57:19.586 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
‎around the globe.

00:57:20.186 --> 00:57:22.355 line:90% position:50% align:center size:80%
